                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined,</hi> I was written to by Mr. Hamer, request<lb></lb>ing I would send some goods from my warehouse in Queen-street—I went there, and saw Horner—I asked for Mr. Hamer, and Homer introduced Morris to me as Mr. Hamer—I said our terms were ready money—Morris said that would not suit him as his capital was all locked up, and he could not pay till after Christmas—I said that would not do, we could not execute the order. <hi rend="largeCaps">MORRIS</hi>—<rs id="t18421128-237-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
